### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test1@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Login to retrieve Access Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test1@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Get validated user profile (use access token from login response)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJFUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IjhhYjU0MjAxLWQ5YTUtNDE2Zi04MTllLWFjNTg0Yzk4YmI3NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..RVoQlHT6OAC7yMSw0GZKRq9PUVO5NlsiFMF1cAzMGRJCtHdpYvjByacWAOAf3v-zNVxhIhems1o_qrIoK1mbVQ
Accept: application/json

### Logout to revoke the session
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{login.data.session.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
